Fabio Alves | fabioalves101@gmail.com | http://blog.gamezombie.com.br | @fabioperalves

A mini-framework written in PHP by @fabioperalves to simplify the twitter login with OAuth 1.0A.

Disclaimer: This project is a work in progress and may contain bugs.

It uses the Abraham Williams oauth's library. For more information about the Abraham Williams' library: https://github.com/abraham/twitteroauth